Package com.uco.ucodgt.mvc.model.business.penalty

Class PenaltyDTO

java.lang.Object
com.uco.ucodgt.mvc.model.business.penalty.PenaltyDTO
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable
public class PenaltyDTO extends Object implements Serializable
This class represents a penalty data transfer object (DTO). It encapsulates information about a penalty, including its unique identifier, points, date, quantity, reason, state, client's DNI, worker's DNI, description, place, informed status, locality, and license plate.
